{"tid":2021007,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法媒報道中國透過馬耳他駐比利時大使館刺探歐盟情報","createTime":"2020-05-17T12:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T13:09:30.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"96a53e9bf0b363d6130f38a2f0042c9b670cee42","tid":2021007,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T12:48:18.000Z","msg":"報道指中國透過馬耳他使館刺探歐盟情報 中方責純屬捏造<br />\n17.05.2020 20:42<br />\n<br />\n法國傳媒報道，比利時與英國情報部門懷疑中國利用馬耳他駐比利時大使館，對鄰近的歐盟委員會總部進行間諜活動。馬耳他否認報道，指完全錯誤；中國駐比利時大使館亦指報道缺乏事實根據，純屬捏造，企圖通過「炒冷飯」來吸引眼球，誤導及欺騙讀者。<br />\n<br />\n法國《世界報》日前報道，馬耳他政府在2004年以2100萬歐元購入一幢大樓作大使館，並獲中方資助買傢俱及翻新，英國情報部門在2010年已警告比利時，憂慮中方趁翻新工程時在使館內安裝監聽設備。不過馬耳其駐歐盟前大使否認，指大使館安裝高標準的安全設備，並定期由馬耳其保安部門檢查。另有外交消息認為現時傳出這篇報道，可能與馬耳他政府決定不再參與，針對利比亞武器禁運的海上任務有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288081&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1288081%26csid%3D261_341&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCVc%2F7AvELiRjmt2A4bWGPaQ%3D&h=bacdae0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288081&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"c31970e3f36b98d6d0d9be3cac75029b8fc068c2","tid":2021007,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T12:49:04.000Z","msg":"【立會要初選 「三不投」聯署】：<br />\n<a href=\"http://legcopetition.wixsite.com/form\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flegcopetition.wixsite.com%2Fform&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCVc%2F7AvELiRjmt2A4bWGPaQ%3D&h=284a231a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">legcopetition.wixsite.com/form</a>"},{"pid":"78bbb3291993de166557b2c725f7d1c8b5563b60","tid":2021007,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"以色列走得太前"},{"pid":"59bdccb13f3ea8b49b3541495552cfa597f35661","tid":2021007,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T12:59:54.000Z","msg":"too late